title: Dan & Tom Searle from Architects
itunes:title: Dan & Tom Searle from Architects
description:
Not only are these dudes my first international guests, but some of the only twins I know playing music in the same band together. Dan & Tom Searle from Architects (in the UK) stayed up late one night to discuss gossip oriented press, their humble beginnings and preconceived notions .
